oples Festival in Danville, Virginia; for the North American release, the album cover was changed to an image of shelves stacked with records. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/Fatboy+Slim/You%27ve+Come+A+Long+Way+Baby\">Read more on Last.fm</a>. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply."}}}